Class DirectedGraph.Node<T>

java.lang.Object
org.jsweet.transpiler.util.DirectedGraph.Node<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of object hold in the graph
Enclosing class:
DirectedGraph<T>
public static class DirectedGraph.Node<T> extends Object
An object representing the nodes of the graph.

It stores elements and remembers edges.

Author:
Renaud Pawlak
